        The animal kingdom is a secret weapon for Scrabble players. With high-value tiles hiding in creature names like ZYZZYVA, BUZZARD, and JACKDAW, knowing which animals are valid in SOWPODS can unlock massive scores. We verified all 30 words below with correct tile values — no guesswork, no inflated numbers.
