      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Champions (20+ Points)</h2>

      <p>These are the elite animal words — scoring 20 or more points from tile values alone, before any premium squares. Landing one of these on a Double or Triple Word Score can swing an entire game.</p>

