              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Points</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Meaning</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">1</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">ZYZZYVA</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">43</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A tropical weevil (the last word in many dictionaries)</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">BUZZARD</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">28</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A large bird of prey</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">3</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">JACKDAW</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">24</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A small crow-like bird</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">HIPPOPOTAMUS</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">23</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A large semi-aquatic mammal</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">FOXHOUND</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-400 font-bold">22</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A dog bred for fox hunting</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Key Insight</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">ZYZZYVA requires a <span class="text-white font-medium">blank tile</span> since only two Z tiles exist in a standard set. Even using one blank (worth 0), the remaining tiles still score 33 points — more than any other animal word at face value.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Strong Picks (14–19 Points)</h2>

