      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Best Points-Per-Letter</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">ZEBU (15pts ÷ 4 letters = 3.75 pts/letter), LYNX (14pts ÷ 4 = 3.5), HAWK (14pts ÷ 4 = 3.5) — short words with premium tiles dominate efficiency.</p>
